<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6464] reportTableInFlux() throws NPE when no table is returned.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6464</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;reportTableInFlux() gets all tables not in flux. However, when no table is found in getTable(numSkipped) function, it will return null. Then, errorReporter attempts to print the table number, which causes a NPE here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
